<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_123" id="61v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_123_line_1576739400002_482">Heincʒen von Bertheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_123_r1l12"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Heincʒ als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . wıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> knecht nehſt ʒu <expan>Heılprunn<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r1l13">nach eẅch gefragt <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd daʒ eẅch <expan>fürkome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey daʒ Jr nıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r1l14">ſıcher vor vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſeyt von der nom <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe vns Geılbrecht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r1l15">von Püchıs tet etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>knecht<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r1l16">niht <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> nach eẅch <expan>ʒufrage<ex>n</ex></expan> . VVan wır mıt dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>Geılbr<ex>echt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r1l17">vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_123" id="61v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Heinczen von Bertheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Heincz, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> knecht nehst zu
                                <expan>Heilprunn<ex>en</ex></expan> nach ewch gefragt
                                <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und daz ewch <expan>fürkome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sey, daz ir niht sicher vor uns und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> seyt
                        von der nom <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> die uns Geilbrecht von Püchis tet
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>knecht<ex>en</ex></expan> niht <expan>befolhe<ex>n,</ex></expan> nach
                        ewch <expan>zu frage<ex>n</ex></expan>, wan wir mit dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Geilbr<ex>echt</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
